txt.en: With one of Viznak's plans proven 'good enough,' you are almost ready to make the climb to Seregost.
Strong vines can be found in the trees near Seregost.\n\nYou should cobble together a rope from the vines.
Viznak can be found near Seregost in eastern Agarnaith.\n\nYou should talk to Viznak and complete your mission in Seregost.
'Sticky stuff works! Almost ready. You too heavy for sticky stuff though, so need rope for you.'

'Phew! We made it out by the skin of our teeth. Those Nurnhoth were certainly in the right to be frightened of Seregost. And what we learned... this plague might be the single greatest threat to the west in Mordor.\n\n'We need to go back, and soon, to disrupt Lhaereth's frightful plans. Otherwise, we might all be in serious trouble. We will find a way to contact you when our forces are ready to strike. For now, a well-earned rest!'
Rhadrog can be found in Viznak's hideout.\n\nYou should talk to Rhadrog.
'Got rope, got sticky stuff. Now, it's time to climb! Ready?'
TBD Standby as Gobbo climbs the wall!
